    {
      "level": 1,
      "text": "To find the result of mixing ing1 and ing4, apply the mixing rule: scan colours R\u2192G\u2192B in order. The first colour where both ingredients share the same sign determines the result potion. If all three colours have opposing signs, the result is neutral."
    },
    {
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Step through each colour:\n  R: ing1=R- (ing1 R?: (sign undetermined)), ing4=R- (ing4 R?: (sign undetermined))\n      \u2192 SAME sign - \u2192 R- resolves."
    },
    {
      "level": 3,
      "text": "ing1=Nnp, ing4=NNN. Mix result: G-."
    },
    {
      "level": 4,
      "text": "To find the result of mixing ing2 and ing3, apply the mixing rule: scan colours R\u2192G\u2192B in order. The first colour where both ingredients share the same sign determines the result potion. If all three colours have opposing signs, the result is neutral."
    },
    {
      "level": 5,
      "text": "Step through each colour:\n  R: ing2=R+ (ing2 R?: (sign undetermined)), ing3=R+ (ing3 R?: (sign undetermined))\n      \u2192 SAME sign + \u2192 R+ resolves."
    },
    {
      "level": 6,
      "text": "ing2=PPP, ing3=pnP. Mix result: R+."
    },
    {
      "level": 7,
      "text": "To find the result of mixing ing7 and ing8, apply the mixing rule: scan colours R\u2192G\u2192B in order. The first colour where both ingredients share the same sign determines the result potion. If all three colours have opposing signs, the result is neutral."
    },
    {
      "level": 8,
      "text": "Step through each colour:\n  R: ing7=R+ (ing7 R?: (sign undetermined)), ing8=R- (ing8 R?: (sign undetermined))\n      \u2192 opposite signs \u2192 skip.\n  G: ing7=G+ (ing7 G?: (sign undetermined)), ing8=G+ (ing8 G?: (sign undetermined))\n      \u2192 SAME sign + \u2192 G+ resolves."
    },
    {
